        <updateDate>2015-03-26T18:20:33Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Secure Rural Schools and Payment in Lieu of Taxes Repair Act </strong></p> <p>This bill extends the Secure Rural Schools and Community Self-Determination Program through FY2016 at FY2011 funding levels. This Program provides payments to state jurisdictions to compensate for the cost of providing services in tax-exempt federal lands within such jurisdictions. </p> <p>The bill also eliminates the fiscal year limitation on funding for the Payments in Lieu of Taxes Program. This program compensates local governments for tax revenue lost due to tax-exempt federal lands within their boundaries. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
